    'compare.supVsRib.ribPropDesc': 'Superior abrasion resistance (3x polyester). Higher tensile strength. Higher moisture absorption (4%).',
    'compare.supVsRib.ribPortDesc': 'More hydrophilic than polyester. Greater moisture regain can be uncomfortable against skin unless specially treated.',
    'compare.supVsRib.ribCostDesc': '$1.50-$4.00 per yard. Premium fiber with higher raw material costs and more complex processing.',
