    'compare.ribVsDinghy.r9a': 'Excellent',
    'compare.ribVsDinghy.r9b': 'Moderate',
    'compare.ribVsDinghy.r10': 'Drape',
    'compare.ribVsDinghy.r10a': 'Good (structured drape)',
    'compare.ribVsDinghy.r10b': 'Excellent (soft drape)',
    'compare.ribVsDinghy.r11': 'Edge Curling',
    'compare.ribVsDinghy.r11a': 'Minimal',
    'compare.ribVsDinghy.r11b': 'May curl at edges',
    'compare.ribVsDinghy.recTitle': 'Which Should You Choose?',
    'compare.ribVsDinghy.recDesc': 'Choose woven fabric if you need dimensional stability, high tensile strength, and abrasion resistance for structured garments, upholstery, or industrial textiles. Choose knit fabric if you need stretch, comfort, and softness for activewear, casual apparel, or body-hugging garments. Many textile products combine both constructions in different layers or panels.',
    'compare.ribVsDinghy.aiBlock': 'Comprehensive comparison between woven and knit fabric constructions. Woven fabrics feature warp and weft interlacing, minimal stretch, high tensile strength, excellent durability, dimensional stability, moderate breathability, excellent abrasion resistance, good drape, and minimal edge curling. Knit fabrics feature interlocking loops, high stretch (15-40% in both directions), moderate tensile strength, good breathability, excellent elastic recovery, soft drape, and potential edge curling.',
    'compare.supVsKayak.title': 'Cotton vs Polyester →Which Fabric Is Right for You?',
    'compare.supVsKayak.desc': 'Compare cotton and polyester fabrics across breathability, durability, cost, care, and use cases. Find the right textile for your needs.',
    'compare.supVsKayak.headline': 'Cotton vs Polyester →Which Fabric Is Right for You?',
    'compare.supVsKayak.short': 'Cotton vs Polyester',
    'compare.supVsKayak.heading': 'Cotton vs Polyester Fabric',
    'compare.supVsKayak.subtitle': 'A practical comparison to help you choose the right fabric for your application, performance needs, and budget.',
    'compare.supVsKayak.col1Title': 'Cotton',
    'compare.supVsKayak.col2Title': 'Polyester',
    'compare.supVsKayak.stability': 'Breathability:',
    'compare.supVsKayak.stabilityDesc': 'Natural fiber allows excellent air circulation. Comfortable against skin for extended wear. Ideal in hot, dry climates.',
    'compare.supVsKayak.speed': 'Moisture Absorption:',
    'compare.supVsKayak.speedDesc': 'Highly absorbent (up to 27% of dry weight). Absorbs sweat away from skin but stays wet, causing discomfort during physical activity.',
    'compare.supVsKayak.storage': 'Durability:',
    'compare.supVsKayak.storageDesc': 'Moderate strength. Prone to shrinking and wrinkling. Can mildew if stored damp. Susceptible to UV degradation.',
    'compare.supVsKayak.learning': 'Care:',
    'compare.supVsKayak.learningDesc': 'Machine washable but shrinks. Requires ironing. Color fading with repeated washing.',
    'compare.supVsKayak.bestFor': 'Best for:',
    'compare.supVsKayak.bestForDesc': 'Casual wear, bedding, towels, denim, home textiles, environmentally conscious consumers (organic cotton).',
    'compare.supVsKayak.kayakStabilityDesc': 'Less breathable than cotton in natural state. Engineered wicking finishes improve moisture management for active use.',
    'compare.supVsKayak.kayakSpeedDesc': 'Hydrophobic ?absorbs only 0.4% of dry weight. Wicks moisture to surface for evaporation. Stays dry during activity.',
    'compare.supVsKayak.kayakStorageDesc': 'Strong, abrasion-resistant. UV-resistant options available. Resists shrinking, stretching, and mildew. Holds shape after washing.',
    'compare.supVsKayak.kayakLearningDesc': 'Machine washable. Quick drying. No ironing needed. Colorfast. Resists wrinkles and stains.',
    'compare.supVsKayak.kayakBestForDesc': 'Sportswear, outdoor gear, uniforms, workwear, technical textiles, performance apparel, travel clothing.',
    'compare.supVsKayak.tableTitle': 'Quick Decision Guide',
    'compare.supVsKayak.kayakShort': 'Polyester',
