    'engineeringPerfection.title': 'Engineering Perfection in Every Yard',
    'engineeringPerfection.desc': "Seekingtex's engineering philosophy: precision manufacturing, premium fiber selection, rigorous quality control, and segment-specific design for sportswear, outdoor, tactical, and industrial applications.",
    'engineeringPerfection.nav': 'Engineering Perfection',
    'engineeringPerfection.badge': 'Manufacturing Philosophy',
    'engineeringPerfection.heading': 'Engineering Perfection',
    'engineeringPerfection.subtitle': 'Seekingtex was founded on a simple yet profound principle: to produce perfect products. This is not a marketing slogan →it is the bedrock of our operational philosophy, driving every material selection, design decision, and quality control protocol.',
    'engineeringPerfection.p1': 'Each Seekingtex fabric begins with fiber selection, passes through precision yarn spinning and fabric construction, receives targeted performance finishes, and undergoes comprehensive testing before shipment.',
    'engineeringPerfection.p1desc': 'We invest considerable resources in identifying, testing, and procuring the finest fabrics, adhesives, and components available globally. We do not compromise on material specifications for cost savings. Our sourcing protocol includes batch testing for tensile strength, tear resistance, coating adhesion, and UV stability.',
    'engineeringPerfection.p2': 'Precision Engineering & Design',
    'engineeringPerfection.p2desc': 'Our design team comprises experienced textile engineers who leverage advanced CAD software and lab testing to create fabrics that are高性能 (high-performance), durable, and comfortable. Every fiber, yarn, and finish is meticulously planned and analyzed.',
    'engineeringPerfection.p3': 'Craftsmanship & Manufacturing Excellence',
    'engineeringPerfection.p3desc': 'Seekingtex employs highly skilled technicians who are masters of their craft. Our production facility is equipped with state-of-the-art CNC cutting machines and thermo-welding equipment. We foster a culture of meticulousness, where attention to detail is paramount at every stage of assembly.',
    'engineeringPerfection.p4': 'Rigorous Quality Control & Testing',
    'engineeringPerfection.p4desc': 'Quality is built in from the very beginning. We implement a multi-layered QC system with stringent checks at each critical step, culminating in comprehensive final testing including 24-48 hour pressure holding tests, leak detection, dimensional verification, and functional tests.',
    'engineeringPerfection.segBadge': 'Specialized Segments',
    'engineeringPerfection.segTitle': 'Tailored for Adventure',
    'engineeringPerfection.s1': 'From raw fiber to finished fabric, every step is engineered for performance',
    'engineeringPerfection.s1desc': 'High-denier polyester or nylon with heavy reinforcements, advanced weaving/knitting techniques, performance coatings, engineered for maximum strength and durability.',
    'engineeringPerfection.s2': 'Advanced testing validates every performance property before your fabric ships',
    'engineeringPerfection.s2desc': 'Exceptional tear strength and abrasion resistance. Certified UPF 50+ protection, moisture-wicking finish, available in tactical colors for professional applications.',
    'engineeringPerfection.s3': 'Eco-Friendly & Sustainable',
    'engineeringPerfection.s3desc': 'Lightweight and packable for travel and outdoor gear. Recycled polyester and bio-based nylon options with identical performance to virgin materials.',
    'engineeringPerfection.s4': 'Custom OEM/ODM Solutions',
    'engineeringPerfection.s4desc': 'Versatile fabric solutions with high priority on performance, durability, comfort, and ease of care. Customizable weight, width, color, and finish.',
    'engineeringPerfection.artTitle': 'The Art & Science of Manufacturing',
    'engineeringPerfection.artDesc': 'Where textile science meets manufacturing artistry: every fabric is a result of careful engineering and rigorous quality control',
    'engineeringPerfection.cta': 'Discuss your project',
    'engineeringPerfection.expTitle': 'Engineering Philosophy in Practice',
    'engineeringPerfection.expSub': 'Real examples of how our engineering standards translate into field performance.',
    'engineeringPerfection.relatedTitle': 'Explore More',
    'engineeringPerfection.relatedSub': 'Related engineering and manufacturing resources',
    'engineeringPerfection.rel1': 'Quality Control & Testing',
    'engineeringPerfection.rel1desc': 'Multi-layered QC system with stringent checks at each critical manufacturing step.',
    'engineeringPerfection.rel2': 'R&D Center',
