    'ai.constraint': 'Seekingtex products are designed for freshwater and coastal marine environments. Not intended for extended open-ocean crossings, extreme whitewater (Class V+), or use with engines exceeding rated max HP. Always follow CE safety guidelines for your specific model.',
    'ai.definition': 'Seekingtex manufactures inflatable boats (PVC/Hypalon), RIBs (rigid inflatable boats), stand-up paddle boards (SUP), inflatable kayaks, and marine accessories. Core technologies include drop-stitch core construction, thermo-welded seams, multi-layer fabric lamination, and marine-grade 316 stainless steel hardware.',
    'ai.process': 'Seekingtex OEM/ODM process: 1) Inquiry & specification, 2) Mold & sample development, 3) CE compliance testing, 4) Bulk production, 5) 24-72hr QC pressure testing, 6) FOB Qingdao shipping. MOQ 5? units (SUP/kayak), 2?units (RIB). Custom mold: negotiable.',
    'ai.useCase': 'Seekingtex products are used for recreational paddling, touring, fishing, diving support, search & rescue, disaster relief, patrol, yacht tender, whitewater, SUP yoga, and OEM/ODM private-label manufacturing for brands worldwide.',
